#### Subphase 3D: Performance Tests (Days 4-5)

**Task 3D.1: Benchmarks (4h)**
```bash
# Performance Targets (measured on standard environment)
Environment: MacBook Pro 16GB M1 (or CI/CD equivalent)
Tool: autocannon
Duration: 60 seconds per test
Concurrency: 10 clients
Timeout: abort if any request >30s

Performance Targets:
├─ Cold start (first request): <2s
├─ Warm response (p95, after 100 warm-up): <500ms
├─ Warm response (p99): <2s
├─ Memory per instance: <50MB
├─ Memory for 10 concurrent: <200MB
├─ Throughput: 10 req/sec maintained
└─ No memory leaks after 1000+ sustained requests

Measurement Command:
  npm run benchmark -- --concurrency 10 --duration 60

Success Criteria:
  ✓ p95 <500ms (warm)
  ✓ p99 <2s (warm)
  ✓ Memory <50MB
  ✓ No memory leaks
  ✓ Throughput ≥10 req/sec
```

